Well, I have been waiting to buy this for my daughter for Christmas. Her and her boyfriend of 8 years watched it all the time. He died Christmas last year, so I thought I would get this to surprise her. She has been watch it online (youtube) every night. So I've been watching to see if the price was going to come down for black Friday but damn. To my surprise it went from 39.99 to 59.99. Wow....That is totally not right or fair to your loyal customers. If you will check my history you will see, we buy ALOT of things from your site but that will soon be changing.. This is not fair at all.......Very upset and disappointed......
